   - Measurement: Annual incident reports
   - Payment: 0.25% per percentage point reduction (max 1%)

3. Energy Efficiency Gains:
   - Target: 10% reduction in municipal energy consumption
   - Measurement: Utility bill analysis
   - Payment: 0.1% per percentage point reduction (max 0.5%)

