   - Target: 80% satisfaction with infrastructure quality
   - Measurement: Annual citizen survey
   - Payment: 0.05% per percentage point above 70% (max 0.5%)

Independent Verifier: [Third-party engineering firm]
Measurement Frequency: Annual
Payment Timing: 90 days after verification report
```

